reviewText: For having a bunch of promises about how well it'll work, this bottle is only about a two-week supply, and it makes no difference in anything--sweat, breath, etc. Save your money and just use perfume and lots of soap and mints!

This supplement is awesome!!! It completely removes all types of body odor including feminine odor issues. It is very effective for me. I didn't have any abnormal body odor issues but I want to be as odor-free as possible. I recommend this to all my friends for the ultimate body deodorant. It is amazing how it makes your poo green!
I dont like this stuff at all. I dont feel fresh. I have tried other brand that actually works. I will be going back to that one. Very disappointed :-(

I really cant tell a difference in this product, have been taking it daily, it arrived on time as expected, that is the only reason I gave this a three star, other than that, it deserves a one for product. doesn't work,

Noticed results after about 4 days. Feces is grass green & odor has been reduced. I have noticed a difference in body odor. I still get it, just not as strong. I've been taking 4 a day & am over weight.
